♂, T1, dorsal aspect 
<emphasis id="1EEA50321F07A146692D143F862DF226" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">K</emphasis>
♀, ovipositor sheath, lateral aspect 
<emphasis id="B14CD33ACE92406553925C9845903DF9" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">L</emphasis>
